The vertical bar in the title block is black in all ASME journals. Since the asmejour class is only for preprints, we include the [fun] option to have the bar in color. Any color name recognized by the xcolor package [
1
] may be invoked by including the option [barcolor=name] in the \documentclass[..]{asmejour} command. The color for this example is Goldenrod3. To have a black bar, either omit barcolor entirely or use the name black.

